[en_US]
Power/Enhanced power

Hacker: Creamymami[EGCG]

Description:
AV Mode: 
- Start with Power max. 
- Get power up on a valid attack or being attacked.
EX Mode: 
- Get maximum power by pressing 'A+B+C'.
- Get maximum power after being attacked.

[zh_CN]
能量模式/能量模式加强

修改者: Creamymami[EGCG]

说明: 
(AV)出来能量为最大，一次攻击与被攻击加一个能量
(EX)按A+B+C与被攻击后能量为最大。

[zh_TW]
能量模式/能量模式加強

修改者: Creamymami[EGCG]

說明: 
(AV)出來能量為最大，一次攻擊與被攻擊加一個能量
(EX)按A+B+C與被攻擊後能量為最大。

